Name: typing_inspection
URL: https://github.com/pydantic/typing-inspection
Revision: 8db011350942f33ac4b5d7db60d4d9ea83ab480f
Version: 0.4.2
License: MIT
License File: src/LICENSE
Description: typing-inspection provides tools to inspect type annotations at runtime.

Upgrading the version of typing_inspection is done by bumping the version of pydantic in
//manifests/third_party/pylibs/requirements.in and then running
//manifests/third_party/pylibs/update-pylibs.sh.
